&lt;li&gt;DoDI S-5240.09 requires Combatant Commanders to identify requirements that may be satisfied through Offensive CI operations (OFCO). Combatant Commanders are further required to identify, nominate, and process passage material (PaM) that supports CCMD goals, plans, and objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
