&lt;li&gt;Develops identify and/or work with CCMD staff to develop PaM, which supports USINDOPACOM requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinates and deconflict PaM with other CCMDs, component commands, sub-unified commands, and service sub-component on a daily basis to attain operational feedback and validation of requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serves as an advisor for the command on all Offensive CI Operations passage material matters to include training, intelligence oversight, coordination, and document review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answer ad-hoc tasking in reference to passage material from USINDOPACOM CCICA andJ2X.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Archive passage material into SAP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
